  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK381">
<l>paṭaikuṭi kūḻamaiccu naṭpara ṇāṟu</l>
<l>muṭaiyā ṉaracaru ḷēṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who possesses these six things, an army, a people, wealth, ministers, friends and a fortress, is a lion among kings.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
